title: Kina Thai - Tornby
typeOfFood: Japanese, Thai, Buffet, Delivery, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Second location of a sushi and Thai food restaurant. Located in Tornby retail park. The vegetarian sushi is vegan suitable as are two other mains: fried vegetables with cashew nuts and Thai vegetable curry with coconut milk. Staff speaks English and know about the ingredients. Free Wi-Fi.
